title: About
text: My name is Alan Tao, and this website is a project I made in Kane’s Free Data Science Bootcamp. I’m really interested in music in general, so I decided to focus my project on this topic. Making this website took a lot of effort because bayseian regression models take a long time to run. Please support me by viewing my work and also my YouTube Channel.

title: Spotify Songs v2
text:
Introduction
This is a deeper analysis of spotify songs using the 30000 Spotify Songs dataset. This is an extension to the exploratory analysis of Spotify songs: Spotify Songs v1.
